Text: Thank you for all the great comics you upload here. But: have you cancelled scanlating the Valhalla comics or can we expect further scanlations soon?

They are coming, but it takes time. #7 is in retexting at the moment, so are The Snow Queen and Inspector Canardo 4 :)
And will go on scanning Valhalla 8 and so on as soon as i get #7 back.
Ah great, thank you, I'm looking forward to it.
My friend,It's good to see you here too.Keep up the good work. :)
